Package imagingbook.lib.util.resource

Class ResourceLocation.Resource

  • java.lang.Object
    • imagingbook.lib.util.resource.ResourceLocation.Resource
  • Enclosing class:
    ResourceLocation
    public class ResourceLocation.Resource
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of this class represent individual resources contained in a particular ResourceLocation. This is a non-static class, since ResourceLocation.Resource instances can only exist in the context of a ResourceLocation.
